It's an interview with Stephen
Levine and Ondrea Levine,

00:16:05.010 --> 00:16:07.400 align:middle line:10%
and the episode is
called "Relationship--

00:16:07.400 --> 00:16:12.190 align:middle line:10%
A Pathway to Self-Discovery."

00:16:12.190 --> 00:16:15.430 align:middle line:10%
>> We wait to be safe to
let go, and therefore,

00:16:15.430 --> 00:16:20.200 align:middle line:10%
