experience that no state

00:16:20.200 --> 00:16:22.510 align:middle line:10%
of mind is preferable
to any other--

00:16:22.510 --> 00:16:23.710 align:middle line:10%
to the heart.

00:16:23.710 --> 00:16:25.180 align:middle line:10%
Only to our self-image.

00:16:25.180 --> 00:16:27.340 align:middle line:10%
To the heart, it's
all just one thing.

00:16:27.340 --> 00:16:29.560 align:middle line:10%
It's all just the
flow unfolding.

00:16:29.560 --> 00:16:31.420 align:middle line:10%
It's all just the
divine presence.

00:16:31.420 --> 00:16:33.160 align:middle line:10%
It's all sacred.

00:16:33.160 --> 00:16:37.870 align:middle line:10%
One of the things we learned
from our relationship,

00:16:37.870 --> 00:16:41.230 align:middle line:10%
as it expanded and expanded,
more than anything else,

00:16:41.230 --> 00:16:47.490 align:middle line:10%
was that love is the only
rational act of a lifetime.

00:16:47.490 --> 00:16:52.420 align:middle line:84%
>> Love is the only
rational act of a lifetime.

00:16:52.420 --> 00:16:54.940 align:middle line:90%
How did that phrase hit you?

00:16:54.940 --> 00:16:56.170 align:middle line:90%
It struck me very deep.

00:16:56.170 --> 00:16:58.800 align:middle line:90%


00:16:58.800 --> 00:17:01.590 align:middle line:10%
That which we believe
in and want to commit to

00:17:01.590 --> 00:17:05.880 align:middle line:10%
wants to come into the world,
but it needs an act to do it.

00:17:05.880 --> 00:17:09.329 align:middle line:10%
And that's where the final
piece of the puzzle comes in--

00:17:09.329 --> 00:17:10.650 align:middle line:10%
art.

00:17:10.650 --> 00:17:12.780 align:middle line:84%
Art is the way we
bring forth all

00:17:12.780 --> 00:17:16.050 align:middle line:84%
of our abstract ideas
and beliefs and concepts,

00:17:16.050 --> 00:17:18.569 align:middle line:84%
and bring them into
this concrete moment

00:17:18.569 --> 00:17:20.339 align:middle line:90%
that we call the now.

00:17:20.339 --> 00:17:21.930 align:middle line:90%
It's an artistic moment.

00:17:21.930 --> 00:17:25.530 align:middle line:84%
All the things we say, the way
we say them, the things we do,

00:17:25.530 --> 00:17:28.740 align:middle line:84%
the way we dress up
our body, how we eat,

00:17:28.740 --> 00:17:31.020 align:middle line:84%
how we talk, how
we sing, the things

00:17:31.020 --> 00:17:33.210 align:middle line:84%
we like, the things
we don't like--

00:17:33.210 --> 00:17:36.700 align:middle line:84%
all of these things show up
in actions and behaviors.

00:17:36.700 --> 00:17:38.620 align:middle line:90%
This is the art of life.

00:17:38.620 --> 00:17:40.585 align:middle line:90%
This is the artist in us.

00:17:40.585 --> 00:17:42.210 align:middle line:84%
And it's a very
beautiful thing, and it

00:17:42.210 --> 00:17:46.180 align:middle line:84%
completes the whole
ecosystem of consciousness.

00:17:46.180 --> 00:17:50.910 align:middle line:84%
Now, this is important, because
all ecosystems are holistic.

00:17:50.910 --> 00:17:53.610 align:middle line:84%
Like the way the
Asian cultures believe

00:17:53.610 --> 00:17:58.420 align:middle line:84%
about truth is holistic,
it's a balancing act.

00:17:58.420 --> 00:18:02.880 align:middle line:10%
But if, for some reason,
science, philosophy, religion,

00:18:02.880 --> 00:18:06.350 align:middle line:10%
and art are at odds
with one another,

00:18:06.350 --> 00:18:10.430 align:middle line:10%
then consciousness and the
cycle of it is not complete,

00:18:10.430 --> 00:18:13.430 align:middle line:10%
and the ecosystem will
start to suffer from it.

00:18:13.430 --> 00:18:17.390 align:middle line:10%
The scientist may not understand
the artist or the religious,

00:18:17.390 --> 00:18:18.420 align:middle line:10%
and vice versa.

00:18:18.420 --> 00:18:22.580 align:middle line:84%
Anyway you mish and mash,
those four elements--

00:18:22.580 --> 00:18:24.890 align:middle line:84%
they may not
understand one another,

00:18:24.890 --> 00:18:28.400 align:middle line:90%
but they complete one another.

00:18:28.400 --> 00:18:33.410 align:middle line:84%
They are in balance with one
another in a proper ecosystem.

