It will ripple throughout
eternity, generation

00:20:53.300 --> 00:20:55.320 align:middle line:10%
after generation.

00:20:55.320 --> 00:21:01.110 align:middle line:84%
The seed is small, but
the effect is enormous.

00:21:01.110 --> 00:21:04.120 align:middle line:84%
So here's the big
question I need to ask.

00:21:04.120 --> 00:21:06.930 align:middle line:84%
What is it going to
take for humanity

00:21:06.930 --> 00:21:11.910 align:middle line:84%
to wake up to our actions,
to what we do to the planet,

00:21:11.910 --> 00:21:14.190 align:middle line:90%
and to one another?

