00:21:30.330 --> 00:21:33.570 align:middle line:90%
it's all driven by love.

00:21:33.570 --> 00:21:35.940 align:middle line:90%
Love is the most powerful bond.

00:21:35.940 --> 00:21:39.300 align:middle line:84%
It is strong, and
it is very decisive.

00:21:39.300 --> 00:21:42.930 align:middle line:84%
It has a very strong commitment
to bringing more love

00:21:42.930 --> 00:21:44.020 align:middle line:90%
into this world.

00:21:44.020 --> 00:21:45.120 align:middle line:90%
But that's the thing--

00:21:45.120 --> 00:21:48.270 align:middle line:90%
love does not just arrive here.

00:21:48.270 --> 00:21:51.750 align:middle line:84%
It needs somebody,
like you, to bring it.

00:21:51.750 --> 00:21:54.060 align:middle line:84%
It needs somebody
like you to spread it.

00:21:54.060 --> 00:21:56.790 align:middle line:90%


00:21:56.790 --> 00:22:00.930 align:middle line:84%
Plant those seeds, and start
bringing it into this planet,

00:22:00.930 --> 00:22:05.200 align:middle line:84%
because it is truly the
only medicine that matters,

00:22:05.200 --> 00:22:08.680 align:middle line:84%
and we are in
desperate need of it.

00:22:08.680 --> 00:22:11.900 align:middle line:84%
So with that being said,
here's my challenge for you.

00:22:11.900 --> 00:22:17.430 align:middle line:90%


00:22:17.430 --> 00:22:21.020 align:middle line:84%
I challenge you to do one
thing every single day that's

00:22:21.020 --> 00:22:25.640 align:middle line:84%
illogical, outside of your
realm of rationale, pragmatism.

00:22:25.640 --> 00:22:29.120 align:middle line:84%
Talk to somebody that you
would normally pass by.

00:22:29.120 --> 00:22:31.730 align:middle line:84%
Go to a restaurant that
you would never go to,

00:22:31.730 --> 00:22:33.170 align:middle line:90%
and try something there.

00:22:33.170 --> 00:22:35.840 align:middle line:84%
Whatever it is,
do it specifically

00:22:35.840 --> 00:22:39.530 align:middle line:84%
because it is
illogical, irrational,

00:22:39.530 --> 00:22:41.970 align:middle line:84%
to see what it has
in store for you.

00:22:41.970 --> 00:22:43.880 align:middle line:10%
And the second part
of this challenge

00:22:43.880 --> 00:22:47.925 align:middle line:10%
is to listen for what
intuition might come to us.

00:22:47.925 --> 00:22:49.550 align:middle line:10%
So whether you're
looking for your keys

00:22:49.550 --> 00:22:51.175 align:middle line:10%
and you can't find
them, whether you're

00:22:51.175 --> 00:22:54.230 align:middle line:10%
trying to pick a movie
or a book to read,

00:22:54.230 --> 00:22:57.980 align:middle line:10%
do something where you need
to listen to your intuition.

00:22:57.980 --> 00:23:00.612 align:middle line:90%
Listen for how it might speak.

00:23:00.612 --> 00:23:02.570 align:middle line:84%
And remember that it
might come to you in a way

00:23:02.570 --> 00:23:05.900 align:middle line:84%
that you have no clue that
intuition could actually

00:23:05.900 --> 00:23:07.500 align:middle line:90%
speak in this way.

00:23:07.500 --> 00:23:10.400 align:middle line:84%
So these are your challenges--
do something irrational,

00:23:10.400 --> 00:23:14.103 align:middle line:90%
and listen for your intuition.

